    </p>
  </div>
  <div style="background:#0f0f18;border-left:3px solid #ff0055;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem">
    <h3 style="font-family:'Press Start 2P',monospace;font-size:8px;color:#ff0055;margin-bottom:6px">4 — PS1 / CD-ROM</h3>
