      • <a href="https://csdb.dk" target="_blank" style="color:#ff0055">csdb.dk</a> — demos y homebrews C64<br>
      • <a href="https://spectrumcomputing.co.uk" target="_blank" style="color:#ff0055">spectrumcomputing.co.uk</a> — ZX Spectrum
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

